headline: MetLife Names Nick Nadgauda Global Chief Information Officer
summary: NEW YORK, December 18, 2024--MetLife, Inc. (NYSE: MET) today announced that Nick Nadgauda will join the company as Executive Vice President and Chief Information Officer, effective March 10, 2025. Nadgauda will report to Bill Pappas, Executive Vice President and Head of Global Technology and Operations.
